    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver despite showing its age. The engine starts consistently and the car handles well on the road, though you may notice some cosmetic wear such as minor scratches on the exterior and visible thinning of the upholstery inside. There are a few minor mechanical quirks, such as a noisy cooling fan and a slow power window, but it remains a solid choice for anyone needing affordable, functional transportation.",
